            </span>
        </h3>
        <p class="paragragh text-left pl-1 pl-md-2 pr-1 text-09" dir="ltr">
            We are proud to facilitate the affairs of traders, efficient communication and ideal quality and quantity efficiency from zero to one hundred your export and import processes, including:
        </p>
        <div class="" dir="ltr">
            <div class="row pl-2">
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg ">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">1</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class="mt-2 text-left pl-2">
                        <span class="text-Bold">Contract</span> (in different languages legally)
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">2</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class="mt-2 text-Bold text-left pl-2">
                        Supply
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">3</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class="mt-2 text-Bold text-left pl-2">
                        Specific and general sorting and packaging
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row pl-2">

                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">4</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class="mt-2 text-left pl-2">
                        <span class="text-Bold"> Internal transportation </span> (single-stage and multi-stage)
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">5</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class=" mt-2 text-Bold text-left pl-2">
                        Clearance in all borders and ports of Iran
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">6</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class=" mt-2 text-Bold text-left pl-2">
                        Customs
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row pl-2">
                <div class="general-services col-md-4 my-row mt-3 mt-md-1">
                    <div class="service-number-bg">
                        <div class="service-number mt-2">7</div>
                    </div>
                    <label class=" mt-2 text-left pl-2">
                        <span class="text-Bold"> Do foreign transportation </span>(land and sea) and ....
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="paragragh text-left pl-1 pl-md-2 pr-1 mt-4 mb-5 text-09" dir="ltr">
            We assure the merchants that in the end, the health of the cargo, as soon as possible, we will officially and legally fulfill your requested order with a full cargo guarantee.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="edit-admin pb-5 pl-2 pr-2 pl-md-5 pr-md-5 d-none">
        <hr />
        <a class="btn btn-info mr-auto pl-3 float-left pr-3 mytext-white"><i uk-icon="create-outline"></i>ویرایش</a>
    </div>
</section>


<!--our service section-->
<h3 class="text-center title-h3 our-service-h3 my-center mb-5">
    <span class="my-center">
        Our Services
    </span>
</h3>
<section class="our-service-section my-center pb-5">

    <div class="our-service-container grid my-center">
        <div class="greenCard my-center">
            <div class="whiteCard my-column my-center">
                <img class="my-center mt-5" src="~/img/index/services/marketing-logo.png" />
                <label class="mt-3 text-08"> Marketing of applicants' products  </label>
            </div>
            <i class="next-ser-icon d-none d-md-block absolute" uk-icon="chevron-forward"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="greenCard my-center">
            <div class="whiteCard my-column my-center">
                <img class="my-center mt-5" src="~/img/index/services/air-earth.png" />
                <label class="mt-3 text-08"> Accepting orders of foreign and domestic merchants from all over the world  </label>
            </div>
            <i class="next-ser-icon d-none d-md-block absolute" uk-icon="chevron-forward"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="greenCard my-center">
            <div class="whiteCard my-column my-center">
                <img class="my-center mt-5" src="~/img/index/services/delivery.png" />
                <label class="mt-4 text-08"> Export your products to the destination country of the applicant </label>
            </div>
            <i class="next-ser-icon d-none d-md-block absolute" uk-icon="chevron-forward"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="greenCard my-center">
            <div class="whiteCard my-column my-center">
                <img class="my-center mt-5" src="~/img/index/services/done.png" />
                <label class="mt-3 text-08"> Carrying out affairs of all stages from zero to one hundred from origin to export and import destination   </label>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
